{"tid":646272,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"老女人林志玲低胸搭飛機","createTime":"2018-04-29T01:50:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-29T15:32:19.000Z","uid":72009,"like":302,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"172421fbacc36be191ddd985a4827a044101c241","tid":646272,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T01:50:05.000Z","msg":"林志玲日前現身北京機場，一下車就驚艷許多粉絲，她身穿低胸長洋裝，露出飽滿「碗公奶」。<br />\n「林志玲貼吧後援團」在微博上傳這組照片，林志玲身穿飄逸長洋裝、長版牛仔襯衫，搭配深藍色球鞋，露出深邃事業線，仙氣十足。志玲姐姐不但向粉絲揮手，還親切與粉絲攀談，毫無大明星架子。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180429/640_b87aab004543a48a5cce8d5492e8307d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180429%2F640_b87aab004543a48a5cce8d5492e8307d.jpg&h=4e45f728&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180429/640_701bca43b8bdd03a903845e98cae1a07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180429%2F640_701bca43b8bdd03a903845e98cae1a07.jpg&h=d3c39723&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180429/640_c71c86f88a60d0b2061e31f20ee499c9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180429%2F640_c71c86f88a60d0b2061e31f20ee499c9.jpg&h=ea475b6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3eb3062c5e4e03787f3c03c609ddeafe85afb49","tid":646272,"uid":3109,"like":29,"dislike":14,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T02:01:54.000Z","msg":"方力申.jpg <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw 屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08